Серебро

Solo: (прислал: Sharikopodshipnik and Romero (not latinos), romych_r@chat.ru)
H---------5-------6--6--6--5-----------------------5---------6--6--6--5---------
G--5--5-------------------------7--5--4-----4/5--5---------------------------7--
D-------------7-------------------------------------------7---------------------

Chords:
Am  F  Dm  E

E-----------------0-----------------1-------1---1---1-----0--------------------
